    {
      "text": "Super Goal! 2, known in Japan as Takeda Nobuhiro no Super Cup Soccer, is a soccer video game developed by Tose and published by Jaleco for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It is the sequel to Goal!.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super Goal! 2, conosciuto in Giappone come Takeda Nobuhiro no Super Cup Soccer (武田修宏のスーパーカップサッカー?) è un videogioco sportivo incentrato sul calcio prodotto dalla Jaleco nel 1993 per la piattaforma Super Nintendo Entertainment System.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "スーパーゴール！2は、日本で『武田修宏のスーパーカップサッカー』として知られる、トースが開発し、ジャレコからスーパーファミコン向けに発売されたサッカービデオゲームで、『ゴール！』の続編です。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
